{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 362.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, when the time comes-- you know, you're going as a group, but each one for himself, type of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, try and help each other, but--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, we had-- we had briefings--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Beforehand of this is what we were going to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was not-- we were not the only group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there were-- you know, there were people-- this was an organization that was going on all the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, it was very much improved on later on-- in later war years where people, like Hannah Szenes and other people, you know, parachuted in behind the lines and all that to get people out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this was the beginning of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we proceeded to Vienna, we got there--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just a little-- just a little satchel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, a change of clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A couple of shirts and a bit of underwear and, you know, a spare pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were some personal things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I had my-- my prayer shawl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm saying it in English-- a Tallit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And tefillin and, you know, some photographs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and my mother, I remember, gave me some gold coinage that she had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was some gold coins, which was money, if you like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was just to have something of value in case I might need it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what the other kids had in their thing, you know, but it was-- wasn't a big deal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were met by the person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We then went from Vienna by bus to Graz, which is--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Graz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I'm not quite sure now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I should have looked it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's about 40 kilometers out towards the-- towards the Alps, but towards the Yugoslav border.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
